# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  CyanideX — Environment Configuration
#  Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your credentials.
#  All integrations gracefully fall back to simulated intel
#  data when keys are missing, so the OS runs out of the box.
#
#  ⚠ Never commit real secrets. Keep them only in ".env"
#    (git-ignored). This example file must stay blank.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

